# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI navigation layer & secret-safety (added 2026-06-28)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# MCP server config — may contain tokens/endpoints, never commit
.mcp.json

# Secret / credential file-name patterns.
# NOTE: *password* is intentionally OMITTED — it would hide legitimate
# source files such as apps/backend/scripts/verify-passwords.js and
# verify-demo-user-passwords.js. Do not add it.
*credential*
*credentials*
*secret*
*token*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.crt
*.pfx

# Generated test / coverage / report artifacts (regenerable)
coverage/
**/coverage/
playwright-report/
**/playwright-report/
test-results/
**/test-results/

# Graphify generated outputs (regenerable). Only GRAPH_REPORT.md is trackable.
# graph.json / graph.html / manifest.json / cache are large or regenerable.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md
graphify-out/cache/

# codebase-memory-mcp local index (regenerable)
.codebase-memory/
codebase-memory.db
*.codebase-memory

# AI context layer kept local-only, consistent with AGENTS.md / PROJECT_CONTEXT.md.
# To publish it with the repo instead, delete the lines below (see
# docs/AI_CONTEXT/00_READ_ME_FIRST.md → "Tracking policy").
CONTEXTO.md
CLAUDE.md
PHASE_AI_NAVIGATION_LAYER.md
PHASE_AI_NAVIGATION_TOOLS_COMPLETED.md